Ann,

Don&#39;t worry about it girl. I don&#39;t fight online anymore. I was set back a little that I was singled out for agreeing with Sumption instead of the issue being taken up with Sumption. LOL If someone don&#39;t understand my view point I am glad to explain. My research is hardly affected by any conflicts that may arise on this or any other forum and my friends on the other side have told me to lighten up a bit and to be patient so I try. The other members of the small circle to which I belong can attest to that. LOL 

