because of me, let me just say that I think a lot of what we were

collectively arguing about may be semantics. We&#39;re all agreed about

pursuing this research in a positive frame of mind. If you have a

naturally positive one, or if you need to do something ritualistic to

remind yourself that you are in a positive mindset, it really doesn&#39;t

matter. The same end is obtained.We&#39; re all okay, no matter which way

